text: Vilcashuamán Airport is a very high elevation airport serving the town of Vilcashuamán in the Ayacucho Region of Peru. The runway has rising terrain in all quadrants. ==See also== * * *Transport in Peru *List of airports in Peru ==References== ==External links== *OpenStreetMap - Vilcashuamán *SkyVector - Vilcashuamán Category:Airports in Peru Category:Buildings and structures in Ayacucho Region
